🧸 5. String Templates (Better String Building)
👶 Problem:

Building strings is messy:

"Hello " + name + " your age is " + age

😵 Hard to read

🆕 Solution:

Java 21 introduces String Templates

👉 Cleaner like:

Hello {name}, age {age}
🧠 Use Case:
Logging
SQL queries
API messages

✅ Example (Java 21)
String name = "Sree";
int age = 25;

String msg = STR."Hello \{name}, your age is \{age}";

👉 Output:

Hello Sree, your age is 25
